dataIdInfo.idAbs: Shows Environmental Value Zones described in Environmental Protection (Water and Wetland Biodiversity) Policy. These areas are used to define environmental values and water quality objectives. These areas were previously know as 'subcatchments' though they were not actual hydrological subcatchments. For further information please refer to the EPP Water website: https://environment.des.qld.gov.au/management/water/policy
